{
  "texts": [
    "The Λ polari- zation provides information on the mean values of quark polarization, whereas the 00 provides information on the correlation of quark and antiquark polarization inside the vector meson [201].",
    "Thus measurements of vector meson spin alignment provide a novel way for probing the quark spin correlations.",
    "This information may also be accessible via the measurements of hyperon-hyperon and hyperon-antihyperon spin correlations [201].",
    "These different scenarios open an exciting discovery potential for the spin polarization measurements.",
    "For example, the strong force correlation may be expected to provide new information about the short distance structure of QGP and the nature of QCD phase diagram [202,203]."
  ]
}